headline: Pivot Energy and Tapestry, Inc. Announce Completion of Three Illinois Community Solar Projects
summary: Pivot Energy, a leading national renewable energy provider and independent power producer, and Tapestry, Inc. (NYSE: TPR), a global house of iconic accessories and lifestyle brands uniting the magic of Coach and Kate Spade, are celebrating a milestone in their partnership. Today, Pivot announced the completion of three Illinois community solar projects, totaling 13.475 megawatts (MWac).
